  "title": "Lead Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Overview: </strong>We are hiring multiple dynamic Lead Engineers to manage different scopes of work including:<br>\n(a) Street Lighting Maintenance<br>\n(b) Commuter Facilities Maintenance<br>\n(c) New Street Lighting Installations<br>\n(d) New Commuter Facilities Works</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervise and lead day-to-day technical and operational activities.</li>\n  <li>Implement and execute approved work plans, drawings, and risk assessments.</li>\n  <li>Ensure accuracy of updates in CWMS and CFEMS systems.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with OCC for fault response and reporting.</li>\n  <li>Manage work teams, subcontractors, and ensure safety compliance.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Engineering with <strong>minimum 3 years</strong> of experience in similar works; OR</li>\n  <li>Diploma in Engineering with <strong>minimum 5 years</strong> of experience; OR</li>\n  <li>ITE Certification with <strong>minimum 10 years</strong> of experience.</li>\n  <li>Strong working knowledge of CWMS, LTA codes, and infrastructure works.</li>\n</ul>",
